WEBVTT

00:12.210 --> 00:18.410
[2009]

00:13.800 --> 00:14.400
Chuan.

00:15.880 --> 00:16.480
Chuan.

00:16.960 --> 00:19.760
Yan Bin invited us to his house
for dinner tonight.

00:20.670 --> 00:21.280
Chuan!

00:23.160 --> 00:24.160
Chuan!

00:24.920 --> 00:26.070
Chuan!

00:36.150 --> 00:37.410
You little crazy girl.

00:37.560 --> 00:38.840
You're going too far.

00:38.960 --> 00:40.820
Wearing earplugs wasn't enough—

00:40.960 --> 00:42.280
now you're taping them shut?

00:42.280 --> 00:43.580
Am I really that annoying?

00:43.580 --> 00:45.190
Well, you chirp non-stop
as soon as you get home.

00:45.190 --> 00:47.120
Don't I have to protect my hearing?

00:47.160 --> 00:48.600
Is your hearing more important or am I?

00:48.600 --> 00:49.520
Oh, spare me.

00:49.840 --> 00:51.200
For such a freebie question,

00:51.200 --> 00:52.260
go ask Jiang Cheng.

00:56.110 --> 00:57.600
As a sniper,

00:57.920 --> 01:00.030
ears are as important as eyes.

01:00.430 --> 01:01.170
Okay, okay.

01:01.200 --> 01:02.090
I'll tape it up for you.

01:02.090 --> 01:03.620
Seal it tight. Tape it well.

01:04.069 --> 01:04.790
You can't hear now, right?

01:04.790 --> 01:05.650
You can't hear.

01:06.630 --> 01:07.230
Chuan,

01:08.920 --> 01:10.310
you really are a big fool.

01:10.310 --> 01:11.230
A big idiot.

01:11.710 --> 01:13.170
You're really something.

01:24.039 --> 01:24.789
Chuan,

01:25.070 --> 01:26.840
are current anti-sniper detection devices

01:26.840 --> 01:28.500
already very well developed?

01:29.280 --> 01:30.560
Theoretically,

01:30.870 --> 01:31.920
as long as you fire a shot,

01:31.920 --> 01:33.690
your position can be quickly locked onto.

01:33.690 --> 01:36.280
You might not even have the chance
to fire a second shot.

01:36.280 --> 01:36.870
Chuan,

01:37.240 --> 01:39.770
isn't it very dangerous
for you to be a sniper?

01:40.300 --> 01:41.130
I think

01:41.160 --> 01:42.360
current devices

01:42.380 --> 01:43.910
cannot replace human ears.

01:44.600 --> 01:45.330
Dad is right.

01:45.680 --> 01:47.440
Situations on the battlefield
are ever-changing.

01:47.440 --> 01:48.350
Having a good pair of ears

01:48.350 --> 01:50.150
is the best anti-sniper system.

01:52.229 --> 01:52.920
Chuan,

01:53.120 --> 01:54.680
your new sniper rifle...

01:55.509 --> 01:56.710
Are you done?

01:57.330 --> 01:59.530
How about you four cops living together

01:59.640 --> 02:00.920
in the future?

02:02.340 --> 02:03.090
Mom!

02:04.220 --> 02:04.810
Mom.

02:04.840 --> 02:06.500
Your cooking is so delicious.

02:06.760 --> 02:07.970
It's so delicious, Mom.

02:07.970 --> 02:08.560
It's very tasty.

02:08.560 --> 02:09.560
Let's talk about something else.

02:09.560 --> 02:11.020
Then that sniper rifle...

03:33.900 --> 03:39.500
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:39.840 --> 03:42.250
[Episode 14]

03:43.240 --> 03:44.970
Before the Jingang operation,

03:45.120 --> 03:47.079
Leader Yao once confided in me.

03:48.079 --> 03:49.810
There's an undercover officer

03:50.410 --> 03:52.280
inside Old Scorpion's
criminal organization—

03:52.280 --> 03:53.750
codename "Cangfeng."

03:54.520 --> 03:56.980
I had a single-line contact
with him before.

03:57.900 --> 03:58.690
Cangfeng?

04:00.310 --> 04:01.360
So this time,

04:01.680 --> 04:03.140
the trade at Jingang Wharf

04:03.490 --> 04:05.640
was intel sent back by Cangfeng.

04:06.840 --> 04:08.440
From the current situation,

04:08.710 --> 04:10.830
he might have been exposed
a long time ago.

04:10.830 --> 04:11.590
So this time,

04:11.650 --> 04:12.560
the rescue

04:12.700 --> 04:14.160
isn't just for Leader Yao—

04:14.510 --> 04:15.840
it's also for Cangfeng.

04:16.560 --> 04:17.430
Cangfeng?

04:17.589 --> 04:18.990
Is it possible that he...

04:20.200 --> 04:20.829
Bad news!

04:21.360 --> 04:22.160
What's wrong?

04:22.630 --> 04:24.310
Two male bodies were found
in the eastern suburbs.

04:24.310 --> 04:25.240
One of them

04:25.340 --> 04:26.740
might be Team Leader Yao.

04:43.830 --> 04:44.680
Professor Jiang.

04:44.680 --> 04:45.360
Senior.

04:45.390 --> 04:46.500
How's the situation?

04:46.500 --> 04:47.720
The investigation is basically done.

04:47.720 --> 04:49.310
We were waiting for you
to come take a look.

04:49.310 --> 04:51.420
The two bodies were discovered
by a local resident

04:51.420 --> 04:52.159
while collecting seafood along the shore.

04:52.159 --> 04:54.190
The forensic doctor's preliminary judgment
is that they were shot at close range,

04:54.190 --> 04:55.390
then tied together

04:55.390 --> 04:56.180
and dumped here.

04:56.180 --> 04:57.480
A handgun was found at the scene,

04:57.480 --> 04:58.620
and fingerprints have been lifted

04:58.620 --> 05:00.560
and sent back to the station for analysis.

05:00.560 --> 05:02.120
So far, only one identity
has been confirmed—

05:02.120 --> 05:03.270
Leader Yao Weihai.

05:03.570 --> 05:04.970
What about the other one?

05:05.000 --> 05:06.460
It can't be confirmed yet.

05:07.010 --> 05:08.020
Where is the gunshot wound?

05:08.020 --> 05:09.150
The back of the head.

05:58.520 --> 05:59.050
Leader.

05:59.070 --> 05:59.470
Okay.

06:05.200 --> 06:06.200
This way, please.

06:08.110 --> 06:08.660
Mr. Wan.

06:09.360 --> 06:09.890
Mr. Wan.

06:11.430 --> 06:12.360
What's going on?

06:12.560 --> 06:13.880
I saw you earlier this morning,

06:13.880 --> 06:15.610
and you brought them along too.

06:16.190 --> 06:17.920
The Jingang operation failed.

06:18.400 --> 06:20.700
The higher-ups have sent
an investigation team down.

06:20.700 --> 06:21.900
Be careful recently,

06:22.450 --> 06:23.490
but don't stress—

06:24.040 --> 06:26.500
just stay calm.
It's nothing to panic about.

06:27.430 --> 06:29.160
After Leader Yao went missing,

06:29.750 --> 06:32.210
I immediately launched a rescue operation.

06:33.250 --> 06:34.200
Normally,

06:35.070 --> 06:35.930
when criminals

06:36.260 --> 06:37.520
take a police officer,

06:37.630 --> 06:39.360
it's to use them as leverage

06:40.430 --> 06:42.630
to negotiate with higher authorities.

06:43.040 --> 06:44.600
So at first,

06:44.909 --> 06:46.770
I still held onto a sliver of hope,

06:47.120 --> 06:48.600
waiting for their call.

06:49.870 --> 06:50.830
But later,

06:52.280 --> 06:53.210
Professor Jiang

06:53.850 --> 06:55.710
came up with a more accurate idea.

06:56.190 --> 06:58.650
I thought the target
was Leader Yao himself.

06:59.210 --> 07:00.870
Let's just call it intuition.

07:02.710 --> 07:04.910
That's what I told Chief Tan at the time.

07:04.980 --> 07:06.440
The time limit is 48 hours.

07:07.000 --> 07:08.630
If we couldn't rescue him

07:08.840 --> 07:10.160
within 48 hours,

07:10.970 --> 07:13.230
then Leader Yao and his undercover agent

07:13.530 --> 07:15.190
would both be in grave danger.

07:16.680 --> 07:18.540
Before the operation, Leader Yao

07:18.720 --> 07:20.520
also knew there were huge risks.

07:20.890 --> 07:22.260
I can understand why Leader Yao

07:22.260 --> 07:23.860
didn't want to retreat then.

07:24.110 --> 07:26.090
Once everything was set in motion,
it was hard to pull back.

07:26.090 --> 07:28.090
When we first planned the takedown,

07:28.360 --> 07:29.720
we were cautious,

07:30.120 --> 07:32.050
but we also had high expectations.

07:32.720 --> 07:33.800
Leader Yao and I

07:33.800 --> 07:36.260
verified the vessel information together,

07:37.560 --> 07:38.800
and at that time, the intel

07:38.800 --> 07:39.860
was very accurate.

07:41.159 --> 07:43.270
After Chief Tan finished his call
with Leader Yao,

07:43.270 --> 07:44.480
we didn't waste a second

07:44.480 --> 07:46.280
and moved in to provide support.

07:46.310 --> 07:48.000
We regrouped with Wan

07:48.000 --> 07:49.270
to capture He Wu.

07:49.480 --> 07:50.430
No one expected

07:50.430 --> 07:52.600
that Old Scorpion
would be right there with them.

07:52.600 --> 07:54.040
This is completely different

07:54.040 --> 07:55.970
from what we knew at the beginning.

07:57.210 --> 07:58.800
The news we got at first was

07:58.830 --> 08:00.870
that Old Scorpion
would appear at the pier.

08:00.870 --> 08:02.480
So when something happened to Leader Yao,

08:02.480 --> 08:03.610
I initially thought

08:03.800 --> 08:05.510
he met Old Scorpion at the pier.

08:05.510 --> 08:07.570
Later I figured out what was going on.

08:07.800 --> 08:09.560
I was shot by a sniper at the time

08:09.600 --> 08:10.530
and got injured,

08:10.800 --> 08:12.750
so I didn't participate in
the subsequent pursuit.

08:12.750 --> 08:14.310
Fortunately, Zhou Jin reacted quickly

08:14.310 --> 08:15.440
and dragged me back.

08:16.190 --> 08:18.250
Otherwise, I would have been killed.

08:18.950 --> 08:21.280
When Leader Yao was ambushed,
there was a lot of smoke.

08:21.280 --> 08:22.540
The scene was chaotic.

08:22.930 --> 08:23.950
Our surveillance system

08:23.950 --> 08:25.550
lost its picture for a while.

08:26.000 --> 08:27.400
Although it wasn't long,

08:27.560 --> 08:28.290
we didn't see

08:28.320 --> 08:29.880
the critical process

08:29.910 --> 08:31.640
of Leader Yao being taken away.

08:31.830 --> 08:33.260
All the situations were reported

08:33.260 --> 08:34.990
by the front-line action team.

08:36.000 --> 08:38.080
At the moment of the explosion, Leader Yao

08:38.080 --> 08:39.840
was dragged into the underground tunnel.

08:39.840 --> 08:40.539
We killed

08:40.570 --> 08:43.169
the 4 criminals
covering the tunnel entrance.

08:44.150 --> 08:45.510
They detonated the bomb

08:45.510 --> 08:47.370
in the underground tunnel again,

08:47.790 --> 08:49.550
causing our action team members

08:49.550 --> 08:51.010
to almost be buried alive.

08:52.510 --> 08:53.510
A total of 6 people

08:54.270 --> 08:56.330
were injured in the whole operation.

08:58.120 --> 08:59.360
There is also a

08:59.840 --> 09:00.630
policewoman who had a direct encounter

09:00.630 --> 09:02.480
with the enemy sniper.

09:04.360 --> 09:05.510
At that time, we already knew

09:05.510 --> 09:06.840
Leader Yao was missing.

09:07.320 --> 09:08.720
What I was thinking about

09:08.910 --> 09:10.670
was how to hold off the gang

09:10.840 --> 09:11.970
and wait for backup.

09:12.480 --> 09:13.680
We were outnumbered.

09:13.750 --> 09:15.240
The sniper took a shot from concealment,

09:15.240 --> 09:16.480
which caused someone on our side

09:16.480 --> 09:17.810
to get injured quickly.

09:18.030 --> 09:19.230
I had made a judgment.

09:19.390 --> 09:20.960
If we kept dragging it out like this,

09:20.960 --> 09:21.960
it was very likely

09:22.000 --> 09:24.550
to turn into a situation
where they use the injured
to ambush our backup.

09:24.550 --> 09:26.270
It was very disadvantageous for us.

09:26.270 --> 09:27.930
My brother used to be a sniper.

09:28.600 --> 09:30.800
He taught me how to locate by listening.

09:31.180 --> 09:33.510
I was somewhat confident I could find him.

09:35.080 --> 09:35.750
Then

09:36.120 --> 09:37.510
why did you go alone?

09:38.750 --> 09:40.610
The fight had already broken out.

09:40.630 --> 09:43.030
A frontal assault required more manpower.

09:43.510 --> 09:45.000
Under those circumstances,

09:45.000 --> 09:46.260
I had to be the one to go.

09:46.390 --> 09:47.790
And my position was good.

09:48.320 --> 09:50.150
Going alone made me a small target,

09:50.150 --> 09:51.750
making it hard to be spotted.

09:52.960 --> 09:54.550
But it did worry the team.

09:56.320 --> 09:58.980
As one of the officers
injured on the front line,

09:59.360 --> 10:00.960
where do you think

10:01.320 --> 10:02.670
the biggest problem

10:02.670 --> 10:04.730
in the command of this operation lay?

10:05.240 --> 10:07.100
Getting injured was my own fault.

10:07.750 --> 10:08.240
Okay.

10:08.670 --> 10:09.800
Your part ends here.

10:09.960 --> 10:10.840
You can go back.

10:15.370 --> 10:15.840
What?

10:16.880 --> 10:18.340
You have something to say?

10:20.120 --> 10:20.980
Just one thing.

10:22.120 --> 10:24.080
Please trust Chief Tan,

10:24.360 --> 10:25.670
and Nancheng Branch.

10:25.910 --> 10:27.030
No one

10:27.240 --> 10:29.370
wants to solve the case more than we do.

10:38.780 --> 10:40.060
That won't do.

10:40.990 --> 10:42.540
You are the person in charge,

10:42.540 --> 10:43.640
the leader of the task force.

10:43.640 --> 10:45.700
How can you make the arrest yourself?

10:46.130 --> 10:47.250
Cangfeng

10:48.010 --> 10:49.250
is still inside.

10:50.790 --> 10:52.520
Only I can coordinate with him.

10:52.620 --> 10:55.360
Provincial Bureau
leaders will come to supervise.

10:55.360 --> 10:56.820
You'll be responsible for

10:56.850 --> 10:58.850
the overall command

10:59.510 --> 11:01.020
and coordination of this operation.

11:01.020 --> 11:01.690
Tan,

11:02.580 --> 11:03.300
please.

11:11.550 --> 11:12.200
Look.

11:12.910 --> 11:15.170
His fatal wound is a shot
to the left chest

11:15.200 --> 11:16.480
that went straight through the heart.

11:16.480 --> 11:19.280
Leader Yao's situation
is much more complicated.

11:19.440 --> 11:22.240
There are traces of
a cyanide capsule in his teeth.

11:22.720 --> 11:24.150
It's hard to determine

11:24.320 --> 11:26.480
whether he bit it himself

11:26.580 --> 11:28.750
or if it broke accidentally
during the struggle,

11:28.750 --> 11:31.660
especially since he was also shot
in the back of the head around the same time.

11:31.660 --> 11:33.300
The trajectory is from top to bottom

11:33.300 --> 11:34.780
at a 45-degree angle.

11:36.200 --> 11:37.200
Just like Cheng.

11:38.160 --> 11:40.190
Didn't we also find a gun?

11:40.540 --> 11:41.950
After comparative testing,

11:41.950 --> 11:43.150
the bullet in the head

11:43.320 --> 11:44.200
was fired

11:44.220 --> 11:45.340
from

11:45.370 --> 11:46.170
this gun.

11:47.790 --> 11:48.660
Leaving the murder weapon

11:48.660 --> 11:50.020
at the dumping site...

11:51.240 --> 11:52.510
It's another provocation.

11:52.510 --> 11:53.480
Not only that,

11:53.610 --> 11:54.920
we also found

11:55.050 --> 11:56.380
a set of fingerprints

11:56.550 --> 11:57.430
on this gun.

11:58.630 --> 11:59.510
Fingerprints?

12:04.000 --> 12:04.750
Chief Tan.

12:04.970 --> 12:05.600
Zhou Jin,

12:05.910 --> 12:07.310
come to my office right now.

12:07.310 --> 12:07.920
Yes.

12:10.680 --> 12:11.900
I'll go see Chief Tan first.

12:11.900 --> 12:12.460
You go ahead.

12:12.460 --> 12:13.320
I'll stay here.

12:22.750 --> 12:25.010
I want to take a look at
Leader Yao's body.

12:27.790 --> 12:28.510
Come in.

12:37.500 --> 12:38.260
Sir.

12:50.640 --> 12:51.400
Zhou Jin,

12:53.550 --> 12:54.810
you are my apprentice,

12:57.320 --> 12:59.380
and Zhou Chuan's biological sister.

13:01.090 --> 13:02.060
I trust you.

13:04.150 --> 13:04.960
I also believe

13:06.420 --> 13:08.230
you are the most eager to see

13:09.510 --> 13:10.300
the 8.17 Case

13:11.020 --> 13:12.500
solved, right?

13:19.550 --> 13:20.240
Sir,

13:21.950 --> 13:22.750
what's wrong?

13:26.390 --> 13:27.390
I suspect

13:28.470 --> 13:30.070
we have a mole in our team.

13:38.120 --> 13:38.840
Leader Yao

13:39.290 --> 13:41.350
was only recently transferred back,

13:41.730 --> 13:42.540
and this time

13:43.090 --> 13:44.890
he will personally lead the team

13:45.070 --> 13:46.280
to Jingang Wharf.

13:48.120 --> 13:49.850
Only insiders know about this.

13:50.790 --> 13:51.700
But obviously,

13:52.410 --> 13:54.200
they were after Leader Yao.

13:55.270 --> 13:56.280
How could they

13:57.350 --> 13:59.110
know our arrangement so well?

14:00.600 --> 14:02.000
Do you have any suspects?

14:03.640 --> 14:04.880
I can't be sure yet.

14:06.800 --> 14:08.260
I need to think it through.

14:09.390 --> 14:10.720
You and Professor Jiang

14:10.860 --> 14:11.740
must stay alert

14:13.820 --> 14:15.300
and watch your own safety.

14:19.010 --> 14:19.720
Got it.

14:21.580 --> 14:23.310
I didn't call you here for this.

14:26.550 --> 14:28.610
There are two more important things.

14:31.440 --> 14:33.240
The identity of the other victim

14:33.310 --> 14:34.440
has been confirmed.

14:38.910 --> 14:40.310
His name is Meng Junfeng.

14:40.840 --> 14:41.900
The file shows that

14:42.400 --> 14:43.600
during the 8.17 Case,

14:44.360 --> 14:46.140
he had just graduated
from the police academy.

14:46.140 --> 14:47.630
Due to his outstanding performance,

14:47.630 --> 14:50.430
Leader Yao developed him
into an undercover agent

14:50.630 --> 14:53.290
to participate in
the 8.17 Case investigation.

14:53.410 --> 14:55.200
Before the operation, Leader Yao

14:55.200 --> 14:56.630
gave me a note,

14:57.750 --> 14:58.480
saying it was

14:58.680 --> 15:00.480
intelligence sent back by a man

15:00.760 --> 15:01.960
codenamed Cangfeng.

15:02.440 --> 15:03.840
We have reason to believe

15:04.480 --> 15:05.540
that intelligence

15:05.630 --> 15:07.290
was sent back by Meng Junfeng.

15:08.030 --> 15:08.830
I suspect

15:09.600 --> 15:11.860
he actually blew his cover very early on.

15:12.670 --> 15:13.870
The criminal syndicate

15:13.870 --> 15:15.130
took advantage of this

15:15.170 --> 15:17.170
and made him deliver a fake message,

15:17.600 --> 15:18.790
which caused

15:18.790 --> 15:21.190
the failure of our net-closing operation.

15:24.330 --> 15:25.040
Sir,

15:26.750 --> 15:28.000
can I make a request?

15:29.270 --> 15:30.670
Do you have the authority

15:31.270 --> 15:32.930
to check if Jiang Cheng's name

15:34.440 --> 15:35.720
is in the secret file?

15:38.670 --> 15:39.360
Why?

15:41.720 --> 15:43.440
Because that day at the water tower,

15:43.440 --> 15:44.360
he told me

15:45.360 --> 15:47.760
he knew those people
had killed my brother,

15:48.510 --> 15:50.840
and he had no idea
I was Zhou Jin at the time.

15:51.550 --> 15:53.480
He was actually saving the police.

15:55.430 --> 15:57.340
When you told me about Cangfeng,

15:58.150 --> 15:59.750
I wondered if it could be him.

16:02.930 --> 16:04.200
Is it possible that

16:06.870 --> 16:08.530
he is also an undercover agent?

16:08.530 --> 16:09.060
Zhou Jin,

16:11.200 --> 16:13.400
first of all, I understand how you feel,

16:14.360 --> 16:16.090
but I have to be honest with you,

16:16.550 --> 16:18.410
and the truth may disappoint you.

16:20.840 --> 16:21.670
His name

16:23.440 --> 16:25.280
is not in the confidential files,

16:25.280 --> 16:26.710
but it is

16:28.750 --> 16:30.810
in the police fingerprint database.

16:31.000 --> 16:32.020
The forensic examiner

16:32.020 --> 16:33.600
lifted a fingerprint from the gun

16:33.600 --> 16:34.930
used to kill Leader Yao.

16:35.320 --> 16:36.430
After comparison,

16:38.830 --> 16:40.690
it's Jiang Cheng's fingerprint.

17:11.119 --> 17:11.800
Sir,

17:16.660 --> 17:18.460
he used to be a great cop.

17:18.480 --> 17:20.130
I know he was once a cop,

17:20.750 --> 17:22.589
a good one

17:23.069 --> 17:24.829
with an impressive record,

17:25.270 --> 17:27.000
highly valued by his superiors

17:27.400 --> 17:28.750
as a key talent.

17:28.750 --> 17:29.750
But don't forget—

17:30.790 --> 17:32.150
his conduct
became completely unacceptable,

17:32.150 --> 17:33.480
even criminal:

17:35.000 --> 17:35.880
hiding drugs,

17:36.180 --> 17:37.070
soliciting prostitutes,

17:37.070 --> 17:38.530
which led to a three-year prison sentence

17:38.530 --> 17:39.900
and ruined his career.

17:45.330 --> 17:47.790
Now, the criminal organization
he's part of

17:48.190 --> 17:50.160
is involved in organized crime,

17:50.460 --> 17:51.910
and he himself

17:52.480 --> 17:54.460
is suspected of intentional homicide.

17:54.460 --> 17:57.520
I hope you won't let your emotions
get the better of you.

17:58.140 --> 17:59.340
If he contacts you,

18:00.120 --> 18:02.920
you must report to the team immediately.

18:04.420 --> 18:05.480
Do you understand?

18:07.680 --> 18:08.410
Understood.

18:11.360 --> 18:11.960
Zhou Jin,

18:14.880 --> 18:15.680
I believe you.

18:23.940 --> 18:24.870
Leader Yao

18:25.590 --> 18:26.680
and Meng Junfeng

18:27.510 --> 18:28.970
are missing a lot of teeth.

18:29.710 --> 18:31.600
During the autopsy,

18:32.190 --> 18:33.500
I found a large amount of
gravel and tooth fragments

18:33.500 --> 18:35.870
in their stomachs.

18:36.550 --> 18:37.270
These guys

18:37.440 --> 18:38.350
are too cruel.

18:40.610 --> 18:41.720
That's how he is.

18:43.300 --> 18:45.560
Not only does he want the police's lives,

18:45.670 --> 18:47.220
but he also wants to trample on

18:47.220 --> 18:48.680
the dignity of the police.

18:50.500 --> 18:51.630
Can you accurately estimate

18:51.630 --> 18:52.630
the time of death?

18:53.060 --> 18:54.060
Three days ago.

19:06.190 --> 19:07.110
Officer Jiang,

19:08.620 --> 19:10.210
does it feel frustrating

19:09.010 --> 19:14.470
[Day 3 after Jiang Hansheng was captured]

19:12.460 --> 19:14.460
to find out that you're not dead yet?

19:20.870 --> 19:22.590
The police will be here soon.

19:25.210 --> 19:26.470
I highly doubt that...

19:29.430 --> 19:30.590
I will kill you.

19:32.020 --> 19:33.700
I will definitely kill you.

19:37.400 --> 19:39.050
Death is actually not scary.

19:42.350 --> 19:45.010
I wonder if Officer Jiang
has heard this saying—

19:46.550 --> 19:48.550
death is the true beginning

19:49.900 --> 19:51.340
and you will be reborn.

19:52.740 --> 19:53.780
Of course I know

19:55.350 --> 19:57.010
that you don't want to die now.

19:58.500 --> 19:59.830
You must be thinking

20:00.950 --> 20:02.460
that if you died now,

20:05.920 --> 20:08.650
what would happen
to the girl you care about most?

20:10.970 --> 20:13.130
The girl in that pocket watch,

20:13.990 --> 20:15.320
what will happen to her?

20:56.450 --> 21:02.850
[Day 6 after Jiang Hansheng was captured]

21:22.060 --> 21:22.830
Don't touch me!

21:22.830 --> 21:24.350
Don't touch me! Don't come any closer!

21:24.350 --> 21:25.150
It's me.

21:25.170 --> 21:26.260
Don't touch me!

21:26.260 --> 21:26.830
Stay back!

21:26.830 --> 21:27.630
Look closely!

21:30.190 --> 21:30.950
It's me.

21:31.910 --> 21:32.590
It's me.

21:34.700 --> 21:35.430
Listen,

21:35.550 --> 21:36.680
the police are here.

21:36.710 --> 21:37.420
Quick.

21:38.150 --> 21:39.410
Help me untie the rope.

21:40.020 --> 21:41.150
Find a place to hide.

21:43.500 --> 21:44.110
Hurry!

22:02.480 --> 22:03.520
They're back.

22:03.720 --> 22:05.520
They're back.
What should we do?

22:06.150 --> 22:07.150
What should we do?

22:08.150 --> 22:09.080
Don't be afraid.

22:09.460 --> 22:10.260
Trust me.

22:10.460 --> 22:11.430
I'll get you out.

22:19.300 --> 22:19.890
Quick.

22:19.910 --> 22:20.640
Come with me.

22:35.110 --> 22:35.700
Get in.

22:47.260 --> 22:48.460
You must stay calm.

22:49.630 --> 22:50.690
Don't make a sound.

22:51.430 --> 22:52.670
I will get you out.

22:53.460 --> 22:54.790
Wait for me to come back.

22:55.260 --> 22:55.910
Don't go.

22:57.980 --> 22:58.630
Trust me.

22:59.980 --> 23:00.740
Trust me.

24:34.830 --> 24:35.830
Officer Jiang.

24:44.780 --> 24:45.390
Qi Yan,

24:47.150 --> 24:47.910
you lose.

24:50.460 --> 24:51.300
Did I?

24:55.220 --> 24:56.060
Don't move.

24:57.300 --> 24:58.300
Freeze!

25:03.300 --> 25:04.190
Calm down.

25:05.360 --> 25:07.490
I just want to return something to you.

25:16.450 --> 25:17.450
She's beautiful.

25:24.580 --> 25:26.240
Jiang Hansheng, don't shoot!

25:26.330 --> 25:26.890
Don't!

25:27.190 --> 25:28.150
I am Yao Weihai.

25:28.170 --> 25:29.460
Look closely, I'm Yao Weihai!

25:29.460 --> 25:30.020
Don't move!

25:30.020 --> 25:30.870
Officer Jiang.

25:30.870 --> 25:31.260
Calm down!

25:31.260 --> 25:32.420
The police are here.

25:32.420 --> 25:33.300
Don't get worked up.

25:33.300 --> 25:33.950
Listen to them.

25:33.950 --> 25:34.550
Calm down.

25:34.590 --> 25:35.590
I am Yao Weihai.

25:35.590 --> 25:36.780
Look closely, I am Yao Weihai.

25:36.780 --> 25:38.700
I just want to return something to you.

25:38.700 --> 25:39.220
Calm down.

25:39.220 --> 25:39.740
Stay calm.

25:39.740 --> 25:40.870
I'm Yao Weihai.

25:41.410 --> 25:42.150
Don't do it.

25:42.150 --> 25:42.550
Quick!

25:42.770 --> 25:43.440
Calm down!

25:43.460 --> 25:44.980
I'll kill you!

25:52.500 --> 25:53.500
I will kill you!

25:55.100 --> 25:55.670
Zhou Jin.

25:56.670 --> 25:57.670
I'll kill you!

25:58.150 --> 26:00.020
I will kill you!

26:00.110 --> 26:00.910
Qi Yan!

26:01.150 --> 26:02.020
No!

26:41.250 --> 26:42.970
Officer Jiang!

27:57.230 --> 27:57.910
Qi Yan.

28:06.500 --> 28:07.740
Officer Jiang.

28:08.000 --> 28:08.720
No.

28:09.490 --> 28:12.010
I should call you Professor Jiang now.

28:12.740 --> 28:14.000
You still remember me.

28:14.510 --> 28:15.440
I'm quite happy.

28:16.670 --> 28:17.430
How is it?

28:18.630 --> 28:19.780
Is my "welcome gift"

28:21.040 --> 28:21.990
grand enough?

28:24.780 --> 28:26.180
Since you don't respond,

28:27.190 --> 28:28.260
I'll assume you like my

28:28.260 --> 28:29.590
way of greeting.

28:30.390 --> 28:31.720
Why are you still alive?

28:35.260 --> 28:36.260
Professor Jiang,

28:37.910 --> 28:39.780
you asked the wrong question.

28:40.650 --> 28:41.930
You should ask

28:42.700 --> 28:45.060
who the person was

28:46.350 --> 28:48.010
you shot and killed back then?

28:49.460 --> 28:50.150
Who?

28:51.390 --> 28:52.910
If the answer were that easy to reveal,

28:52.910 --> 28:54.430
wouldn't it be too boring?

28:55.460 --> 28:56.660
Same rules as always—

28:57.700 --> 28:59.190
how about a game?

29:03.460 --> 29:04.350
Guess

29:04.740 --> 29:05.700
heads

29:06.260 --> 29:07.110
or tails.

29:07.910 --> 29:08.970
If you get it right,

29:10.350 --> 29:12.080
I'll chat with you a bit longer.

29:50.520 --> 29:52.320
Professor Jiang, you are a bit naughty.

29:52.320 --> 29:53.280
Play with me.

30:35.830 --> 30:36.870
Professor Jiang,

30:37.430 --> 30:38.950
you are very impolite!

30:38.980 --> 30:40.790
Didn't your mother teach you?

30:41.190 --> 30:42.760
Politeness is the rule of communication

30:42.760 --> 30:43.880
between people.

30:44.540 --> 30:46.070
It's unnecessary with you.

30:51.060 --> 30:51.980
What a pity.

30:53.190 --> 30:54.220
I thought there was

30:54.220 --> 30:55.820
some connection between us.

30:56.040 --> 30:57.150
I thought we

30:58.470 --> 30:59.520
were friends.

31:01.500 --> 31:02.300
Right?

31:03.740 --> 31:04.780
I don't know why

31:04.780 --> 31:06.670
every time I show goodwill,

31:07.500 --> 31:08.780
it makes you

31:09.300 --> 31:10.740
hate me

31:11.540 --> 31:12.830
and disgusts me.

31:17.220 --> 31:18.590
What exactly happened?

31:25.060 --> 31:25.860
What's wrong?

31:28.260 --> 31:28.950
Hansheng.

31:30.610 --> 31:31.810
Is that Officer Zhou?

31:32.350 --> 31:33.630
Is that Officer Zhou?

31:36.280 --> 31:38.770
Say hello to Officer Zhou for me.

31:42.160 --> 31:44.220
Officer Zhou.

31:45.360 --> 31:47.150
Who are you? What do you want?

31:47.810 --> 31:48.530
Zhou Jin,

31:48.910 --> 31:49.710
how could you?

31:49.980 --> 31:51.380
It's that sniper, right?

31:51.780 --> 31:53.430
The sniper I chased, right?

31:54.260 --> 31:55.720
How did he get your number?

31:56.390 --> 31:57.500
Why did he call you?

31:57.770 --> 31:58.920
Sir just told me

31:59.220 --> 32:00.460
there was a mole in the team.

32:00.460 --> 32:01.590
I didn't believe it.

32:01.910 --> 32:03.300
He has found you now.

32:03.740 --> 32:05.280
He even has found your number.

32:05.280 --> 32:06.410
What do they want?

32:06.740 --> 32:07.590
Give me the phone.

32:07.590 --> 32:09.590
I... I will go find Bai Yang.

32:23.780 --> 32:24.510
Don't worry.

32:25.500 --> 32:26.340
It's fine.

32:27.460 --> 32:28.150
I'm fine.

32:29.430 --> 32:30.590
Give me your phone.

32:31.670 --> 32:34.070
I'll ask Bai Yang
to check the phone number,

32:34.390 --> 32:35.150
okay?

32:38.430 --> 32:39.390
Don't worry.

32:40.740 --> 32:42.060
No matter who they are,

32:43.500 --> 32:45.220
I will never let them hurt you.

32:48.870 --> 32:49.700
So,

32:51.040 --> 32:52.230
give me your phone.

32:53.830 --> 32:54.780
No need to check.

32:55.700 --> 32:57.020
I know who he is.

32:58.740 --> 32:59.620
He is Qi Yan.

33:04.410 --> 33:05.850
He is Qi Yan?

33:12.190 --> 33:13.190
Professor Jiang,

33:13.700 --> 33:16.020
who the person was

33:16.630 --> 33:18.290
you shot and killed back then?

33:18.500 --> 33:19.190
Hansheng.

33:20.830 --> 33:21.430
Hansheng.

33:23.390 --> 33:24.110
I'm fine.

33:25.060 --> 33:26.590
But if what you said is true—

33:26.980 --> 33:28.260
if he really is Qi Yan—

33:29.300 --> 33:31.700
then who was the one
that got shot back then?

33:34.700 --> 33:35.350
Zhou Jin,

33:36.700 --> 33:38.100
I need to go to Huaiguang.

33:38.800 --> 33:39.930
You want to look into

33:40.070 --> 33:42.400
the serial murder cases from 20 years ago?

33:43.540 --> 33:45.670
Because of some special circumstances,

33:45.670 --> 33:47.350
this investigation in Huaiguang

33:47.350 --> 33:48.610
might not go smoothly.

33:50.430 --> 33:51.390
If possible,

33:52.790 --> 33:54.470
I hope you can stay by my side.

33:54.950 --> 33:55.630
Of course.

33:56.870 --> 33:59.020
Qi Yan just asked you to send his regards;

33:59.020 --> 34:00.150
that's clearly a way

34:00.260 --> 34:02.170
to use your safety to threaten me.

34:03.280 --> 34:05.410
It's too dangerous for you to go alone.

34:05.460 --> 34:07.190
I'll go apply to Sir right away.

34:08.239 --> 34:10.409
Then thank you in advance, Officer Zhou.

34:10.409 --> 34:12.810
You must protect me
and never leave my side.

34:14.940 --> 34:15.670
Don't worry.

34:38.020 --> 34:39.219
This is the work phone

34:39.389 --> 34:40.800
and notebook

34:41.909 --> 34:43.440
that Leader Yao left for me.

34:43.469 --> 34:45.000
I have read them carefully.

34:45.449 --> 34:46.580
Based on

34:47.000 --> 34:48.699
my thoughts over the past few days,

34:48.699 --> 34:49.820
I have 3 ideas

34:50.350 --> 34:51.600
I'd like to report to

34:51.639 --> 34:52.570
all the leaders.

34:53.320 --> 34:55.969
[Deputy Director Lu Zhinan,
Binjiang Provincial Public Security Bureau]

34:53.460 --> 34:54.179
Go ahead.

34:55.090 --> 34:55.739
First,

34:56.350 --> 34:58.020
I suspect there was an internal problem

34:58.020 --> 34:59.750
during the Jingang operation.

35:00.020 --> 35:00.870
Next,

35:01.230 --> 35:03.060
I will conduct an internal investigation

35:03.060 --> 35:03.910
to verify

35:04.220 --> 35:05.410
my guess.

35:05.870 --> 35:06.530
Meanwhile,

35:07.180 --> 35:08.540
I request the municipal bureau's
assistance

35:08.540 --> 35:09.870
in the upcoming search

35:10.140 --> 35:12.620
and capture operations
to enhance operational security.

35:12.620 --> 35:13.230
Second,

35:14.180 --> 35:16.510
before the Jingang operation, Leader Yao

35:16.980 --> 35:17.790
was already

35:18.910 --> 35:19.910
aware of

35:20.830 --> 35:22.870
the possibility of his own sacrifice.

35:22.870 --> 35:23.460
However,

35:24.180 --> 35:25.660
having worked with him

35:25.660 --> 35:26.750
for so long,

35:27.100 --> 35:28.870
I know he wouldn't allow himself

35:28.870 --> 35:31.530
and Cangfeng
to be sacrificed without purpose.

35:31.980 --> 35:34.040
Therefore, there's
definitely more complexity

35:34.040 --> 35:36.570
behind this case
than we initially imagined.

35:36.910 --> 35:37.660
Here,

35:38.870 --> 35:39.870
I'd like to follow

35:40.580 --> 35:42.440
Leader Yao's final instructions

35:42.580 --> 35:44.310
and shoulder the burden of

35:44.310 --> 35:46.110
the 8/17 Case and related cases.

35:47.310 --> 35:48.750
Leaders, please trust me

35:49.590 --> 35:50.920
and give me this chance.

35:52.310 --> 35:53.390
I will consider

35:54.830 --> 35:56.160
this matter carefully.

35:56.390 --> 35:58.020
Tell me your third point first.

35:58.020 --> 36:00.020
The third point is about Jiang Cheng.

36:00.020 --> 36:01.310
Don't jump to conclusions too early

36:01.310 --> 36:02.620
about whether he is a friend or a foe,

36:02.620 --> 36:04.180
dead or alive.

36:04.980 --> 36:05.750
I believe

36:06.580 --> 36:07.980
the fingerprints on the gun

36:07.980 --> 36:09.540
were left in a deliberately obvious way.

36:09.540 --> 36:11.200
The more deliberate it seems,

36:11.350 --> 36:13.710
the more it suggests
countless possibilities.

36:13.710 --> 36:14.950
Therefore, we should treat him

36:14.950 --> 36:16.020
with the same seriousness

36:16.020 --> 36:17.180
as we do Old Scorpion,

36:17.180 --> 36:18.060
Qi Yan,

36:18.210 --> 36:19.440
and

36:20.460 --> 36:21.350
He Wu.

36:22.110 --> 36:26.460
[Huaiguang City]

36:32.790 --> 36:34.180
I went down to the county for a visit,

36:34.180 --> 36:35.180
so I'm not around.

36:35.230 --> 36:36.890
You're already in Huaiguang?

36:37.100 --> 36:38.790
We're already in Xiacheng District.

36:38.790 --> 36:39.440
Alright then.

36:39.440 --> 36:40.910
Find a place to stay first.

36:40.980 --> 36:41.430
Okay.

36:47.950 --> 36:49.280
Prof went to the county.

36:49.660 --> 36:51.660
Mr. Wang went to the county himself?

36:53.060 --> 36:54.180
We can go to

36:54.180 --> 36:55.580
the Xiacheng Branch first.

36:55.580 --> 36:56.100
Perfect.

36:56.100 --> 36:56.910
The hotel I booked

36:56.910 --> 36:58.970
is very close to the Xiacheng Branch.

36:59.100 --> 37:00.540
And looking at the pictures,

37:00.540 --> 37:02.000
it should be pretty clean.

37:03.310 --> 37:04.510
As long as it's clean.

37:07.060 --> 37:08.720
So how many rooms did you book?

37:10.510 --> 37:11.110
One.

37:11.760 --> 37:12.290
Let's go.

37:23.000 --> 37:24.010
It doesn't look

37:24.120 --> 37:25.690
as clean as in the photos.

37:26.500 --> 37:27.360
It's fine by me.

37:47.360 --> 37:48.110
Is it okay?

37:52.550 --> 37:53.110
Okay.

37:57.180 --> 37:59.270
Although he is unreachable
from time to time,

37:59.270 --> 38:00.910
there is definitely a problem this time.

38:00.910 --> 38:02.770
Moving his grandparents' graves

38:02.980 --> 38:04.230
was decided half a year ago.

38:04.230 --> 38:05.100
It's a big deal.

38:05.500 --> 38:06.950
Isn't it abnormal

38:07.180 --> 38:09.510
that he couldn't be found
on the exact day?

38:15.920 --> 38:18.150
[Did Jiang Cheng ask you to do it for him?
Did he call you about the money?]

38:22.870 --> 38:24.020
Nothing at all.

38:24.460 --> 38:26.190
That's why I said he is missing.

38:26.710 --> 38:28.640
His phone is off,
and he's not replying to messages.

38:28.640 --> 38:29.710
I've been looking for him for 3 or 4 days.

38:29.710 --> 38:32.510
I'm telling you,
something definitely happened.

38:45.520 --> 38:47.810
[He'll reply if he wants to contact you.
Listen to me. Stop looking for him.].

38:58.750 --> 38:59.810
What's the matter?

39:03.060 --> 39:04.390
Jiang Cheng is missing.

39:05.140 --> 39:06.470
Yan Bin is very worried.

39:07.660 --> 39:10.860
You didn't say anything to him
about Jiang Cheng, did you?

39:15.750 --> 39:16.620
Do you think

39:18.830 --> 39:19.710
a person

39:19.850 --> 39:20.350
can really

39:20.350 --> 39:21.950
change that drastically?

39:25.800 --> 39:28.000
Humans are creatures of circumstance.

39:28.580 --> 39:29.500
Back then,

39:30.870 --> 39:32.470
I always thought Jiang Cheng

39:33.580 --> 39:34.710
was a kind,

39:35.330 --> 39:36.120
upright man.

39:44.580 --> 39:46.310
To have faith in the one you love

39:46.430 --> 39:47.160
is not wrong.

39:55.540 --> 39:56.200
I loved him,

39:56.800 --> 39:57.930
but it's in the past.

39:59.370 --> 40:00.700
We are police officers.

40:01.270 --> 40:02.060
Everything

40:03.040 --> 40:04.240
depends on evidence.

40:50.500 --> 40:51.230
Jiang Cheng,

40:51.980 --> 40:53.040
give me your hands.

40:53.350 --> 40:54.350
What is this for?

40:55.350 --> 40:56.150
It's the rule.

40:56.380 --> 40:57.310
Always has been.

41:04.100 --> 41:05.760
Be gentle. It hurts, Zhou Jin.

41:09.060 --> 41:09.870
Also,

41:11.310 --> 41:13.110
your eyes need to be blindfolded.

41:13.110 --> 41:14.440
No need to gag me, right?

41:28.300 --> 41:28.870
Done.

41:31.420 --> 41:32.620
You are quite strong.

42:00.450 --> 42:01.850
Why aren't they back yet?

42:03.790 --> 42:04.750
It's already nice of them

42:04.750 --> 42:06.150
to make us two cups of tea.

42:07.470 --> 42:08.930
Are they really that busy?

42:09.390 --> 42:10.140
I'll go ask.

42:10.510 --> 42:11.240
Zhou Jin,

42:11.500 --> 42:12.230
don't.

42:12.750 --> 42:14.080
Even if we're with Prof,

42:14.350 --> 42:15.150
it's the same.

42:16.660 --> 42:17.580
Why?

42:19.180 --> 42:19.980
No matter what,

42:19.980 --> 42:21.270
we are colleagues.

42:21.510 --> 42:23.240
I didn't expect a warm welcome,

42:23.690 --> 42:24.890
but this attitude...

42:28.830 --> 42:29.500
Captain Li.

42:30.660 --> 42:31.750
It really is you.

42:32.950 --> 42:35.130
Wang Pengze left and now you're here.

42:35.380 --> 42:36.010
What?

42:36.180 --> 42:37.180
A revolving door?

42:37.590 --> 42:38.140
Wait,

42:38.390 --> 42:40.030
do you not trust us,

42:40.130 --> 42:41.390
or don't you trust him?

42:42.520 --> 42:43.210
Hello,

42:43.540 --> 42:44.790
a comrade earlier

42:44.810 --> 42:45.910
said he would help us find

42:45.910 --> 42:47.940
the files for the 1997 serial killer case.

42:47.940 --> 42:50.020
But he's been gone for over an hour

42:50.270 --> 42:51.430
and hasn't returned.

42:51.430 --> 42:52.270
Just wait.

42:52.630 --> 42:55.230
This case has gone
back and forth so many times,

42:55.540 --> 42:56.590
there's a ton of material.

42:56.590 --> 42:57.990
We won't bother you then.

42:58.420 --> 42:59.110
Let's go.

42:59.790 --> 43:00.620
Go?
